\dfrac{1}{2}x + \dfrac{x}{e^x -1}
\dfrac{1}{2}x + \dfrac{x}{e^x -1} = - \dfrac{1}{2}x - \dfrac{x}{e^{-x} -1}
f(-x)
f(x)
f(x)=\dfrac{1}{2}x + \dfrac{x}{e^x -1}
=\frac{x(e^x+1)}{2(e^x-1)}
f(x) =\dfrac{1}{2}x + \dfrac{x}{e^x -1} = \dfrac {x(e^x - 1) + 2x}{2(e^x - 1)} = \dfrac{xe^x - x + 2x}{2(e^x - 1)} = \dfrac{xe^x + x}{2(e^x - 1)} = \dfrac{x(e^x + 1)}{2(e^x - 1)}
f(x) = f(-x)
f(x)=\frac{x}{2}+ \frac{x}{e^x-1}
\frac12 \frac{x(e^x-1)+2x}{e^x-1}=\frac12 \frac{xe^x+x}{e^x-1}
f(-x)=\frac12 \frac{-xe^{-x}-x}{e^{-x}-1}\cdot \frac{-e^{-x}}{-e^{-x}}=\frac12 \frac{x +xe^x}{-1+e^x}=f(x)
 - \frac{1}{2}x \ - \ \frac{x}{e^{-x} \ - \ 1} \ = \ - \frac{1}{2}x \ - \ \frac{xe^x}{1 \ - \ e^x } \ = \ - \frac{1}{2}x \ + \ \frac{xe^x}{e^x \ - \ 1} 
 \frac{xe^x}{e^x \ - \ 1} \ = \ x \ + \ \frac{x}{e^x \ - \ 1} 
 - \frac{1}{2}x \ + \ x \ + \ \frac{x}{e^x \ - \ 1} \ = \ \frac{1}{2}x \ + \ \frac{x}{e^x \ - \ 1} 
